name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Superstart 69 - Millions NFT arts in New Tab

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Replace new tab page with beautiful and inspirational artworks based on blockchain NFT technology.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Superstart 69 is a simple Chrome extension for crypto and art enthusiasts who like non-fungible token crafts. Now your new tab page will be more attractive and inspiring showing millions of different NFT artworks from the coolest artists around the world.

Features: 

• New artwork each time you open the new tab  

• Minimalistic visual design without anything superfluous not to distract you 

• Each work has its author's Twitter account and marketplace link to purchase it 

• Dark and Light themes, automatically fitted to your OS

• No need to create an account

• Free of charge  

P.S All content in extension is supervised by our moderator to be safe for users under 18. (Don't worry about opening your Chrome while in public)

—————————

Are you an NFT artist and want to add your NFT work to Superstart 69 extension? Apply via our website [superstart69.com](http://superstart69.com)
